The Story Bridge will be lit White and Green to recognise 2023 Pakistan National Day.

Pakistan National Day is celebrated on 23 March and this light up aims to uplift the Pakistani Australian Community&#39;s recognition and community efforts in beautiful multi-cultural Queensland. &nbsp;

This Light Up is organised by: Pakistan Australian Cultural Association

